  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice — this is a factual stub, not your words. NEEDS A HERO IMAGE: a terminal screenshot. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">A minimalist amber-on-black terminal UI for GitHub PRs, reviews, and checks, written in Rust. It is designed to be complementary to lazygit.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The PR rollup logic in Rust — status glyphs and age coloring\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/github-sloth/code.png\" alt=\"The PR rollup logic in Rust — status glyphs and age coloring\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/github-sloth/code.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/github-sloth/code.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/github-sloth/code.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/github-sloth/code.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The PR rollup logic in Rust — status glyphs and age coloring\" width=\"1400\" height=\"900\" style=\"--splay-rot:1.75deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1400×900\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The PR rollup logic in Rust — status glyphs and age coloring</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The TUI rendering — ratatui layout and styled spans for the PR list\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/github-sloth/code2.png\" alt=\"The TUI rendering — ratatui layout and styled spans for the PR list\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/